name: FindMeaFlight
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: find me a flight
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Do you want to know what the cheapest option for your expected travel is? Ask Find Me a Flight! It will provide you with information about the most affordable flights all around the world.

For example, you can ask about the cost of these flights:

From London to New York
From Boston to Paris
From Prague to Bratislava

Once you provide Find Me a Flight with permission, you can get the result to your e-mail address.
